title: Group Therapy: Is he supposed to be the one for me?
description: A listener is wondering if she should stay with her current boyfriend that she has a child with when she is constantly thinking about a guy she's worked with.  It's the "what if" that is confusing her but her boyfriend is great and loves her and her daughter so much.
